{"tid":1548691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鬼佬中伏】監狗會專家話現況複雜，遠超範疇","createTime":"2019-09-07T05:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T07:23:43.000Z","uid":202464,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"127d0e00bba66a87d0fdb47f2b712b185be67e56","tid":1548691,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】監警會國際專家組主席Sir Denis O'Connor稱，目前香港局勢複雜、令人擔憂，亦遠超於警方及監警會範疇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSir Denis昨晚結束5日的訪港行程，他說，5日內已感受到香港社會處境複雜，「不過即使監警會有多厲害，目前形勢遠超於警方的問題，亦超出監警會的範疇」。<br />\n<br />\nSir Denis認為：「沒有一個行業，願意揭露其行動決策、紀錄和錯誤決定，絕大部分人都喜歡展示自己優秀一面；關鍵是IPCC是否有能力要求警隊提供有關資料。」"},{"pid":"b60c8aed4444c41ec6dbd1d868f98a98777303f0","tid":1548691,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"290dbd270a6b7189aa94b3975c84e0941e422808","tid":1548691,"uid":160964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"佢都話要獨立調查委員會"},{"pid":"f4f1a34c563f1ff8bfc2dd0be562eb1695c67d43","tid":1548691,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40417c27209a06fb497a5518baf737844853e7fb","tid":1548691,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:05:47.000Z","msg":"鬼佬：中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19652df36505293efa7b1b4d1dd7fb117b3acb83","tid":1548691,"uid":22360,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"鬼：屌你要紐倫堡先搞得掂"},{"pid":"e4f6c10b032700277cbb92bec6d4e8be6e38bea8","tid":1548691,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:14:10.000Z","msg":"777想用鬼佬增加監狗會公信力代替獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n如果可以勸到班鬼佬唔同佢癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027e649df82a42fb4abc9be7db9c728f5f435051","tid":1548691,"uid":106026,"